## Geoapify Places API key. Used for real restaurant search + details (built on OpenStreetMap data).
## Get a free key at https://myprojects.geoapify.com/ (free tier: 3,000 credits/day).
## Address geocoding uses OpenStreetMap Nominatim directly and needs no key.
VITE_GEOAPIFY_API_KEY=

## Supabase project credentials. Used for auth, database, and realtime group rooms.
## Get these from your Supabase project settings > API.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

## AI provider key (OpenAI or Gemini). Used for natural-language recommendations and group summaries.
## If left blank, the app falls back to a local rule-based recommendation engine.
VITE_AI_API_KEY=
VITE_AI_PROVIDER=openai
